<emphasis id="D2BEEAA4FF15FF735C5CF812FAAA66C0" box="[1090,1305,1951,1977]" italics="true" pageId="216" pageNumber="217">Marem unicum legi</emphasis>
[I collected a single male]”. According to 
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FF15FF735A05F84EFCA466A7" author="Rivosecchi, L." box="[539,791,1987,2014]" pageId="216" pageNumber="217" pagination="45 - 50" refId="ref365613" refString="Rivosecchi, L. (1987) Note sugli Sciomyzidae. VIII. Sulla Pherbellia majuscula (Rondani, 1877) (Diptera, Acalyptera). Fragmenta Entomologica, 20 (1), 45 - 50." type="journal article" year="1987">Rivosecchi (1987: 46)</bibRefCitation>
, the MZUF specimen of 
<taxonomicName id="27CA4D35FF15FF735C2AF84EFA9766A4" authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1868" box="[1076,1316,1987,2013]" class="Insecta" family="Sciomyzidae" genus="Pherbellia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="216" pageNumber="217" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="majuscola">
